      <title>Version 1.1.3</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<pre>### Fixed
- **Gateway handshake rejected** — Changed `client.id` from `clawdbot-macos` to `gateway-client` to match the gateway protocol schema's allowed client IDs. This fixes connection failures with gateway 2026.3.13+.</pre>]]></description>
